_sText: Players Drop with Awp and Pistol.  Both sides of map are made even.  Boxes seperate one side of map from other.  Use boxes to duck between and dodge the threat of awpers so as to get to middle buy area.  Then try to duck from box to box to kill enemy awpers close range.  Or sit back and use the guard tower, 3 level house w/accessible roof/boxes to pick off enemy from afar.
